data.description: Welcome Home! This Absolutely delightful, Beautifully maintained 4 bedroom 2 bathroom NEW ROOF HOME is ready to be yours! This gorgeous, Open Concept floor plan with recessed lighting has ALL the space you need to relax, work, spend time with family or guests. The Kitchen Boasts with Granite Countertops, Plenty of cabnitry, and a walk in PANTRY! Your Huge granite Island can entertain everyone and make everyone feel included!!! Upon entering the home you will see the the parts of a home that make it home. The first bedroom ( currently being used as an office) Gives great views of the neighborhood and the sunsets. The 2nd bedroom and bathroom have thier own little hallway so you can have the guest have the privacy they need. On the other side of the living room which is perfectly centered for your gatherings, You will Find the Master Bedroom and 4th bedroom. This easy layout is perfect for Nurserys, craft rooms, Man/Woman caves. With all rooms wired to have cable, they can be anything you need. The Master Bedroom and Bathroom are where no expense was left behind. the Master bathroom has both a Jaccuzzi Bathtub, Walk in shower, walk in closet, and 2 Sinks!!! Not to mention how beautiful, young and pristine it is. Outside. If you ever wants to get home, sit down, and relax, you have choices. You can hang out in your clean two car garage,You can watch the cars drive by while sitting on your front porch, with your already clean landscaped yard, or go to your private backyard that is fully fenced and sit on your fully covered back porch, light up the firepit, turn on the T.V., Because its already wired and ready for it. And enjoy yourself. Just minutes from I-4!!! Auburdale itself is one of Central Floridas smallest cities. It has one of Floridas best RV Parks Camp Margaritaville. It also has a cute little downtown.With Resturants, a dog park, a speedway, The Teco trail, boutiques, Elite Cable park, and a historic Muesum. The home is newer in age. The seller is so into detail that they are not missing a beat when it comes to making sure who gets this home is happy.
